Chris Ball took his own life on September 14 last year . 
  He made a final goodbye video to his family and said there was nothing they could have done to stop him . 
  Chris was sent home from hospital with 10 Valium because of a shortage of beds . 
  His mother Kerrie Keepa said he was suffering from depression . 
  His brother Jayden found his body and the video . 
  Chris said in the video that no one should blame themselves for his disease . 
  His family have shared the video to raise awareness of the disease . 
 